  }, "ATMs"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Bureaucracy Busters - Groups tasked with eliminating the small, bureaucratic annoyances that get in the way of work.  Problems are expected to be small enough that they can be solved in less than 6 months with $30k or less."), mdx("li", {
