    parentName: "ol"
  }, "Enjoy! And then go back to #1 and start again.")), mdx("h2", null, "My Take-Aways"), mdx("p", null, "Alright, so now I need to summarize all that into key take-aways for how we want to run Ops Research.  I think the 5 keys I'd focus on are:"), mdx("ol", null, mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ol"
  }, "Define our mission\na. A simple, ambitious, open-ended mission statement that gives work purpose and inspires everyone on the team to come to work every day."), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ol"
  }, "Only hire the best\na. Define a recruiting/hiring process that uses work sampling and structured interviews to find the best candidates\nb. Ensure that management is aligned on the importance of hiring only the best.  If we all agree it is better to have an unfilled position than the wrong person in that position, then we should be good to go."), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ol"
