  }, "Set up learning groups to teach key skills")), mdx("p", null, "These are listed in their order of importance.  We could keep going with more and more ideas from the book, but I think #3 (the survey and team feedback) will be key in finding opportunities for where we want to go next.  Where do team members see opportunities today?  What issues do they want to address? If we can put in place a culture where asking these kinds of questions and making recommendations is encouraged, then the rest should take care of itself.  (And we can always come back to the book later if we run out of ideas...)"));
